    {
      "id": "PopularPost339667",
      "post_content": "A sphinx that discards cards instead of draws them, what?!?   \n  \nIn actuality the discard will only be used in response to a removal spell, so it won't result in card disadvantage and the repeatable scry 3 will increase the value of your draws so much that it will virtually be card advantage. ",
      "posted_by": "Purplerooster",
